\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Weapon and Armor Proficiency:}{\fs20\cf0  Union Sentinels are proficient with all simple and martial weapons, all armor, and all shields. 
\par }{\b\i\fs20\cf0 Sending }{\b\fs20\cf0 (Sp):}{\fs20\cf0  At 1st level, the Union Sentinel gains the use of the }{\i\fs20\cf0 sending }{\fs20\cf0 spell as a spell-like ability once per day, plus one addition
