\par }{\b\i\fs20\cf0 Shield of Law }{\b\fs20\cf0 (Sp):}{\fs20\cf0  At 1st level, the Union Sentinel gains the use of the }{\i\fs20\cf0 shield of law }{\fs20\cf0 spell as a spell-like ability once per day, plus one ad
